&lt;p&gt;&amp;quot;I have come from an area where rainfall is very scarce. It is very hot too. Our houses are made of mud. The walls of the houses are very thick and also plastered with mud. The roofs are made of thorny bushes.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This student must be from a village of&lt;/p&gt;

